### DESCRIPTION
### Makes Iron Bear/Iron Cub use no fuel, so it will only leave if destroyed through 
### damage or if exited by Moze. Note: This mod does not alter action skill cooldown;
### if Iron Bear leaves, it will take the normal amount of time to be usable again.
### 
### TO DO
